      • select

        Autocomplete select(ChoicePicker picker)
        Selects the first suggestion according to the given rules in picker param. In other words, it selects the first suggestion which satisfies the choice picking rules defined in picker
        Parameters:
        picker - for defining the rules by which the suggestion will be selected
        Returns:
        returns back the Autocomplete component.
        Throws:
        RuntimeException - when no such option found
        See Also:
        ChoicePickerHelper.ByIndexChoicePicker, ChoicePickerHelper.ByVisibleTextChoicePicker
